Job Responsibilities:
• Design and develop interactive web applications that enable customers to navigate, uncover valuable insight and tell stories from billions of content items across print, social and broadcast media; 
• Develop reusable front-end components using advance technology like HTML5, LESS, React, Flex, Node.JS and Flexible, serving thousands of corporate customers in the Asia region; 
• Be an integral part of product/engineering group to define, design and build WOW products; 
• Work closely with UX team to ensure technical achievability and accurate implementation of design front-end design solutions; 
• Translate designs and style guides provided by the UX team into functional, stable and high performance user interfaces; 
• Contribute to continuous improvement on user interface, software architecture or new technologies; 
• Stay in current and new web technology trends and front-end developments;

